name: Alien throwing flowers
description:
Releitura da Obra "Soldier throwing flowers" de Banksy
Assim como a Obra original o conceito seria a demonstração de paz social para cada individuo viver de forma livre e sem preconceitos.

Reinterpretation of the work "Soldier throwing flowers" by Banksy
Just like the original work, the concept would be the demonstration of social peace for each individual to live freely and without prejudice.
